          ItemChargeAssignmentPurch, PurchaseLine, ItemChargeAssignmentPurch."Applies-to Doc. Type"::Receipt, PurchRcptLine."Document No.",
          PurchRcptLine."Line No.", PurchRcptLine."No.");
